metadata.description: Wunks are leveling the playing field and changing the game with unique utility, benefits, and community funds. Wunks pave the way for equity of access in the NFT space. We, Wunks, are here to stay with our own style and rocking a whole lot of pink! There are a total of 6,000 Wunks on the blockchain.
